    "It includes codes for profiles, such as painting, expert, and user profiles.",
    "Additionally, it contains codes for various attributes such as emotions, toxicity and biases.",
    "• Metadata.csv: Comma-separated values (CSV) file containing detailed information about each dialogue in the dataset.",
